<<voiceline KristenHappy1>>
Kristen: It’s got fifty-five rides and games and over a hundred different vendors this year, making it <i>the</i> best place to go for fun, food, and above all, trying out new things. Or so I’ve heard, anyway. 
The fair bustles around you, sights and sounds and smells almost overwhelming as people shriek on rides and vendors hawk their wares. 
